txt.en: Within the old ruins of Stramvárth lie abandoned supplies from various Orcs and goblins who have camped there….\n\nYour mission is to collect the abandoned supplies scattered throughout Stramvárth.
You have been tasked with collecting the abandoned supplies scattered throughout Stramvárth.
The mission is complete!\n\nSpeak to Hórin for your reward!

'I have a new mission for you, [placeholder].\n\n'My scouts were passing by the abandoned ruins of Stramvárth in the Floodfells, where they noticed some supplies, just left there! We should return at once and gather any of the supplies that have yet to spoil.'
Monsters in this mission will enrage at low morale, gaining attack strength and attack speed.
Your mission is to collect the abandoned supplies scattered throughout Stramvárth.\n\nSpeak to Hórin to travel to Stramvárth.
'Well done! With these supplies, the war effort will continue! It is important to keep everyone fed and healthy in our quest to reclaim Gundabad.'
